{"title":"Abscesos cerebrales-2024","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Estudios Pivotales/Abscesos cerebrales-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Abscesos\\Ncerebrales","guid":"qD170M7UJqHfi3JmiouIOA","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Abscesos cerebrales: Epidemiología,\\Ndiagnóstico y tratamiento","guid":"h26rOPLNDSQBDQjLR669FQ","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"1. Epidemiología","guid":"3NEm1_7uk5H2gYtqmffwbQ","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"• Incidencia: 0.3-0.9/100,000 hab.\\N(EE.UU. y Europa) [3, 4, 6, 7].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"• Factores de riesgo:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"2","text":"• Inmunocomprometidos: VIH,\\Ninmunosupresores, trasplante [4, 5].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"2","text":"• ↑Hombres (70%), edad\\Npromedio: 34 años [2&&].","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"1","text":"2. Etiología","guid":"tVddvjK42VaoHJGtnudxyQ","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"•\\NMicroorganismos\\Nfrecuentes:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"7","text":"• Bacterias: Staphylococcus y\\NStreptococcus (52%) [2&&].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"7","text":"• Otros: micobacterias, protozoos,\\Nhelmintos, hongos [1&&, 2&&].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"7","text":"• Diagnóstico\\Nmicrobiológico:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"7","text":"• Identificación de patógenos en\\N68% de casos [2&&].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"7","text":"• Cultivos positivos: múltiples\\Nbacterias en 23% de casos [2&&].","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"14","parent":"1","text":"3. Diagnóstico","guid":"WYt7w4GarvCt6N9ey8y-0g","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"• Imágenes:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"14","text":"• RM cerebral con DWI →\\Ntécnica más sensible [1&&].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"14","text":"• Procedimientos\\Ndiagnósticos:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"14","text":"• Aspiración temprana → esencial para\\Nidentificar patógeno [2&&].","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"19","parent":"1","text":"4. Tratamiento","guid":"YIng0FDcDANutSCSlm4TeQ","children":[{"id":"20","parent":"19","text":"• Antibioticoterapia:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"19","text":"• Protocolos específicos\\Nsegún patógeno [2&&].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"19","text":"• Evaluación de tratamientos\\Nmás cortos en estudio [Brouwer\\Ny van de Beek, 2017].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"19","text":"• Intervenciones\\Nquirúrgicas:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"19","text":"• Aspiración estereotáxica → técnica\\Nmínimamente invasiva con baja tasa de\\Ncomplicaciones [2&&].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"19","text":"• Terapias adicionales:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"19","text":"• Oxígeno hiperbárico en evaluación\\N[Brouwer y van de Beek, 2017].","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"27","parent":"1","text":"5. Pronóstico","guid":"AA8e8qA0JEXnw4IzPJKACw","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"• Mejoras en resultados:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"27","text":"• Avances en técnicas de imagen y\\Nprocedimientos neuroquirúrgicos\\N[Brouwer y van de Beek, 2017].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"27","text":"• Tratamiento antibiótico protocolizado\\N[Brouwer y van de Beek, 2017].","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"31","parent":"0","text":"Factores de Riesgo en\\NAbscesos Cerebrales","guid":"6JdMPFa-z5wne4EYm3-nzQ","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"1. Condiciones\\Npredisponentes","guid":"_kPSCOR_7Nit1-pY37SuOA","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"• Diseminación contigua:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"• Traumatismo penetrante","guid":"xDobZ5uooWnsfIC5yO3wGg","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"33","text":"• Neurocirugía","guid":"J9K666cfKoKVMjOG6cYcTg","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"33","text":"• Infecciones de oído y senos\\Nparanasales [1&&, 2&&].","guid":"XGcKjx1sUGNwLfqsg_zR4A","children":[]}]},{"id":"37","parent":"32","text":"• Patógenos asociados:","guid":"ALKQBOg6cOaSwj2ScnaLjA","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"• Staphylococcus aureus","guid":"nRF-fl5FXZ_7j6trc7y_7A","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"37","text":"• Streptococcus\\N(aerobios y anaerobios)","guid":"Smv0fwxByVATY7qZICL4xw","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"37","text":"• Enterobacterias: Klebsiella,\\NProteus, Salmonella [1&&].","guid":"u0e1YqBfKmIt7HDSuo8yFA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"41","parent":"31","text":"2. Diseminación\\Nhematógena:","guid":"BX7u-TGDF_YdpHg9GL-L1w","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"• Asociaciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"• Endocarditis","guid":"9FGp2xpUavzxUGF8fH2S_w","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"42","text":"• Cardiopatía congénita","guid":"albDoin6CfY28LwTkPZqIw","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"42","text":"• Infecciones pulmonares","guid":"CXPhjvWdMbZ2gx47kf9EGA","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"42","text":"• Infecciones\\Ndentales [2&&].","guid":"6Sqp0Yhh_Q8pcg2YgsUMuQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"47","parent":"41","text":"• Patógenos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"• Endocarditis: S. aureus,\\NStreptococcus spp.","guid":"CfpjhrAWMDZcFqn5yWNfXw","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"47","text":"• Infecciones dentales y sinusales: Polimicrobianas\\N(incl. Fusobacterium, Prevotella, Actinomyces,\\NBacteroides, Haemophilus) [2&&].","guid":"ij_N4hwk7NE-mSBp1hPhDw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"31","text":"3. Pacientes con VIH:","guid":"bLfu-VyZ7goUg2ti4nuX2Q","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"• Principal causa: Toxoplasma gondii → múltiples abscesos pequeños.","guid":"7LnAk8K4dwpho7UK7RiTqg","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"50","text":"• Otras causas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"• Nocardia spp.","guid":"CQo17HnXbGBCvdKgFY02dQ","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"52","text":"• Mycobacterium tuberculosis [1&&].","guid":"sK36dYMFGbxMWU7dQgigZQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"55","parent":"31","text":"4. Trasplantes y\\Nneutropenia:","guid":"hWK9MBvUdC8TzNU4__N6gg","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"• Riesgo de abscesos micóticos:","guid":"7d-kbHpPK7SiimNQpap_GQ","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"• Aspergillus","guid":"wNbYKP_GiWdNcB7PMItUnw","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"56","text":"• Candida","guid":"TcOkOXx3wQ_ayraUf-F5Mg","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"56","text":"• Mucorales","guid":"Db2vkHoFcA0s7TCrsLXvnQ","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"56","text":"• Scedosporium [1&&].","guid":"Y25K2_LrGneL-bDKUvPBSQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"55","text":"• Causas bacterianas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"• Enterobacteriaceae: E. coli, Enterobacter, Klebsiella, Proteus, Salmonella [1&&].","guid":"bwdcbn_C7xsC2p4efHheQA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"63","parent":"31","text":"5. Variaciones\\Ngenéticas:","guid":"KpI3gJGuCG7s_vUSCkW6cQ","children":[{"id":"64","parent":"63","text":"• Estudio de asociación genética: Polimorfismos en genes ICAM-1 y MCP-1 → ↑susceptibilidad [8&].","guid":"9wg8FY7GbEvoBDTRqqM7-A","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"63","text":"• Resultados:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"• ↑niveles de ICAM-1 y MCP-1 en muestras de absceso y sangre.","guid":"nI9euJROwOXCxCnall7CoA","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"65","text":"• Validación necesaria en cohortes mayores [8&].","guid":"zwjPWUyiiYE_yKNWdstt0g","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"68","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico de\\NAbscesos Cerebrales","guid":"kxLqiYuTqJl75l8E9kQg7A","children":[{"id":"69","parent":"68","text":"1. Presentación\\Nclínica:","guid":"mJSLYUrohBkQL5WnHHF3Ww","children":[{"id":"70","parent":"69","text":"• Triada clásica: Cefalea (69%),\\Nfiebre (53%), déficits neurológicos\\Nfocales (48%) [2&&].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"69","text":"• Solo el 20% presenta los\\N3 síntomas [2&&].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"69","text":"• Otros síntomas: Cambios en el\\Ncomportamiento, defectos cognitivos sin\\Ndéficits neurológicos focales ni fiebre [2&&].","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"73","parent":"68","text":"2. Imágenes:","guid":"S1zCS1n17pjkw5dyB_Rk8Q","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"• Crucial para el\\Ndiagnóstico: RM y TC [1&&,\\N9].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"73","text":"• TC con contraste IV: Determina tamaño y\\Nnúmero de abscesos; no discrimina entre\\Nmetástasis/tumores [1&&].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"73","text":"• RM: Diferenciación de abscesos de tumores\\Nprimarios, quísticos o necróticos mediante\\Nimágenes ponderadas por difusión (DWI) y\\Ncoeficiente de difusión aparente (ADC) [9].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"73","text":"• DWI: Sensibilidad y especificidad\\Ndel 96% para diferenciar abscesos\\Nde tumores [10].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"73","text":"• Meta-análisis (11 estudios, 504 pacientes,\\N519 abscesos): Sensibilidad del 95%,\\Nespecificidad del 95% [11&].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"73","text":"• Técnicas avanzadas: Espectroscopía\\Nde RM, medición de volumen\\Nsanguíneo cerebral [12, 13].","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"80","parent":"0","text":"3. Métodos\\Ndiagnósticos\\Nadicionales:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"• Evidencia de infección:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"80","text":"• ↑Velocidad de\\Nsedimentación\\Neritrocitaria","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"80","text":"• Leucocitosis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"80","text":"• ↑PCR","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"80","text":"• Meningitis bacteriana\\Nconcomitante: Examen de LCR\\N[2&&].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"80","text":"• Parámetros sanguíneos normales\\Nen 30-40%, recuento de leucocitos en\\NLCR normal en 30%.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"80","text":"• Punción lumbar: Con precaución; 19%\\Nde deterioro por desplazamiento\\Ncerebral, 5% mortalidad [14].","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"88","parent":"0","text":"4. Identificación de focos\\Ninfecciosos subyacentes:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"89","parent":"88","text":"• Ecocardiografía:\\NDescartar endocarditis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"88","text":"• Rx de tórax:\\NInfecciones\\Npulmonares","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"88","text":"• Evaluación de oídos, nariz,\\Ngarganta (sinusitis,\\Nmastoiditis) y dientes [1&&].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"88","text":"• FDG-PET (en pacientes\\Nseleccionados): Identificar focos\\Ndistantes de infección [15].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"88","text":"• Intervenciones: Extracción dental,\\Nreemplazo de válvula cardíaca, cirugía\\Nde senos paranasales [16].","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"94","parent":"0","text":"5. Identificación\\Ndel patógeno:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"95","parent":"94","text":"• Esencial para ajustar\\Ntratamiento antibiótico [1&&, 17].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"94","text":"• Neurocirugía: Aspiración estereotáxica del\\Ncentro purulento del absceso.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"94","text":"• Indicaciones: A menos que haya\\Ncontraindicaciones por el patógeno sospechado\\No condición clínica del paciente [1&&].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"94","text":"• Ejemplo: VIH con sospecha de\\Ntoxoplasmosis → Terapia presuntiva\\Njustificada si anticuerpos IgG positivos.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"94","text":"• Cultivo polimicrobiano o falta de\\Nrespuesta a antibióticos: Considerar\\Naspiración estereotáxica [1&&].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"94","text":"• Drenaje continuo: Puede disminuir la\\Ntasa de reoperación [18].","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"101","parent":"0","text":"6. Investigación\\Nmicrobiológica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"102","parent":"101","text":"• Aspirado de absceso y\\NLCR (si disponible):","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"101","text":"• Tinción de Gram","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"101","text":"• Cultivos aeróbicos y\\Nanaeróbicos [1&&].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"101","text":"• Pacientes inmunocomprometidos o con\\Nfactores de riesgo específicos:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"101","text":"• Tinción y cultivos para\\Nmicobacterias, hongos, Nocardia\\Nspp.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"101","text":"• PCR para T. gondii.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"108","parent":"0","text":"Referencias:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"109","parent":"108","text":"1. Brouwer, M. C., & van de Beek, D. (2017).\\NCurr Opin Infect Dis, 30:129–134. DOI:10.\\N1097/QCO.0000000000000334.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"108","text":"2. Brouwer, M. C., et al. (2014).\\NMeta-analysis on brain abscesses.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"108","text":"3. Estudio prospectivo sobre DWI\\Nen abscesos cerebrales.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"108","text":"4. Estudio en 115 pacientes con\\Nlesiones ocupantes de espacio.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"108","text":"5. Meta-análisis del valor de DWI en la\\Ndiscriminación de abscesos.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"114","parent":"0","text":"12, 13. Estudios sobre\\Ntécnicas avanzadas de RM.","guid":"","children":[{"id":"115","parent":"114","text":"6. Serie de casos sobre\\Npunción lumbar.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"114","text":"7. Indicación de\\NFDG-PET.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"114","text":"8. Intervenciones para\\Neliminar focos de infección.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"114","text":"9. Uso de navegación\\Nestereotáxica en neurocirugía.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"114","text":"10. Beneficio del\\Ndrenaje continuo.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"120","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento de\\NAbscesos Cerebrales","guid":"ou9knPh2cYgaCmbBaGUyUw","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"0","text":"1. Tratamiento\\Nempírico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"122","parent":"121","text":"• Cobertura amplia: Bacterias\\NGram (+) y Gram (-).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"121","text":"• Antibióticos: Cefotaxima o\\Nceftriaxona + metronidazol [2&&].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"121","text":"• Usado en 53% de los\\Npacientes [2&&].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"121","text":"• Pacientes\\Ninmunosuprimidos:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"121","text":"• Añadir voriconazol + TMP-SMX o\\Nsulfadiazina (cobertura: hongos,\\Nlevaduras, toxoplasmosis) [1&&].","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"127","parent":"0","text":"2. Duración de la terapia\\Nantimicrobiana:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"128","parent":"127","text":"• Intravenosa: 6-8\\Nsemanas [1&&].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"127","text":"• Estudios observacionales sobre\\Nduraciones más cortas:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"127","text":"• Termografía + RM DWI para detener tratamiento:\\NPromedio 21 días, recurrencia en 2 pacientes,\\N66% con buen resultado [19].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"127","text":"• Recomendación británica: 1-2 semanas\\NIV, luego cambiar a régimen oral si hay\\Nbuena respuesta clínica [20].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"127","text":"• Tratamiento oral: Ciprofloxacino,\\Nmetronidazol, amoxicilina [21].","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"133","parent":"0","text":"3. Indicaciones para\\Ntratamiento neuroquirúrgico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"134","parent":"133","text":"• Adquisición\\Ndel patógeno:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"133","text":"• Aspiración estereotáxica\\Ndel absceso [1&&].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"133","text":"• Intervención quirúrgica:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"133","text":"• Indicaciones: Localización, tamaño (>2.5\\Ncm sugerido), condición clínica,\\Ndescompresión exitosa [1&&, 23, 24].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"133","text":"• Otras indicaciones: Herniación\\Ncerebral inminente, absceso\\Nperiventricular [1&&].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"133","text":"• Resección completa: Considerar\\Nen abscesos superficiales en áreas\\Nno elocuentes [25&].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"133","text":"• Meta-análisis\\N(208 pacientes):","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"133","text":"• Resección: ↓Reoperación, ↑Limpieza\\Nposoperatoria del absceso, mejora\\Nneurológica en 1 mes.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"133","text":"• Estudios de baja calidad,\\Nsesgo de publicación [25&].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"133","text":"• Resección en casos seleccionados: Patógenos de\\Nlenta o limitada respuesta antibiótica (hongos, TB,\\NActinomyces, Nocardia) [1&&].","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"144","parent":"0","text":"Referencias:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"145","parent":"144","text":"1. Brouwer, M. C., & van de Beek, D. (2017).\\NCurr Opin Infect Dis, 30:129–134. DOI:10.\\N1097/QCO.0000000000000334.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"144","text":"2. Brouwer, M. C., et al. (2014).\\NMeta-analysis on brain abscesses.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"144","text":"3. Estudio retrospectivo sobre\\Nduración de tratamiento.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"144","text":"4. Recomendación de la\\NSociedad Británica de\\NQuimioterapia Antimicrobiana.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"144","text":"5. Regímenes de\\Ntratamiento oral.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"150","parent":"0","text":"23, 24. Indicaciones para\\Nintervención quirúrgica.","guid":"","children":[{"id":"151","parent":"150","text":"6. Meta-análisis comparativo de\\Nresección vs. aspiración.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"152","parent":"0","text":"Tratamientos Adyuvantes en\\NAbscesos Cerebrales","guid":"AMnOTUYViybhAbyfFaAfpQ","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"0","text":"1. Corticoesteroides:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"154","parent":"153","text":"• Uso reportado: 17% de pacientes,\\Nprincipalmente dexametasona [2&&].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"153","text":"• Beneficios: Mejora rápida en casos\\Nde edema perilesional [1&&].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"153","text":"• Riesgos: ↓Penetración de antibióticos a\\Ntravés de la BHE → prolonga duración del\\Ntratamiento antibiótico.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"153","text":"• Recomendación: Solo en edema profundo con\\Ndesplazamiento cerebral significativo que puede\\Nllevar a herniación [1&&].","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"158","parent":"0","text":"2. Terapia de\\Noxígeno\\Nhiperbárico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"159","parent":"158","text":"• Estudios y resultados:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"158","text":"• Serie de casos: 13 pacientes, 5 días de\\Ntratamiento tras aspiración estereotáxica → sin\\Nrecurrencias, sin grupo control [26].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"158","text":"• Estudio retrospectivo (Suecia): 40\\Npacientes, 11 años, mitad tratados\\Ncon oxígeno hiperbárico.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"158","text":"• Resultados: Mejor en grupo tratado, pero\\Ndiferencias en severidad inicial de la enfermedad\\N(GCS) limitan comparabilidad [27].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"158","text":"• Recomendación: Necesidad de más\\Nestudios antes de considerar como\\Ntratamiento de rutina.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"164","parent":"0","text":"Referencias:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"165","parent":"164","text":"1. Brouwer, M. C., & van de Beek, D. (2017).\\NCurr Opin Infect Dis, 30:129–134. DOI:10.\\N1097/QCO.0000000000000334.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"164","text":"2. Brouwer, M. C., et al. (2014).\\NMeta-analysis on brain abscesses.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"164","text":"3. Estudio inicial sobre terapia\\Nde oxígeno hiperbárico.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"164","text":"4. Estudio retrospectivo sobre\\Noxígeno hiperbárico en Suecia.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"169","parent":"0","text":"Complicaciones y Pronóstico de\\NAbscesos Cerebrales","guid":"XbW03vFO8_AMnLyoMo6NEA","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"0","text":"1. Deterioro clínico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"171","parent":"170","text":"• Indicaciones: ↓Nivel de conciencia,\\N↑Déficits neurológicos → Repetir\\Nimágenes cerebrales.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"170","text":"• Detectar: Agrandamiento del\\Nabsceso, hidrocefalia,\\Nherniación inminente [28].","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"173","parent":"0","text":"2. Complicaciones\\Nseveras:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"174","parent":"173","text":"• Ruptura intraventricular:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"173","text":"• Complicación grave:\\NVentriculitis aguda, hidrocefalia.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"173","text":"• Asociación: OR 5.50 para\\Ndesenlace desfavorable [28].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"173","text":"• Mortalidad\\Nreportada: 27-85%\\N[28].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"173","text":"• Hidrocefalia aguda/herniación\\Ninminente: 31% requieren\\Ncirugía repetida [2&&].","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"179","parent":"0","text":"3. Epilepsia:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"180","parent":"179","text":"• Frecuencia: ≥25% de los\\Npacientes durante admisión.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"179","text":"• Tratamiento anticonvulsivo profiláctico: No\\Nevaluado específicamente en absceso cerebral, no\\Nrecomendado rutinariamente [29].","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"182","parent":"0","text":"4. Pronóstico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"183","parent":"182","text":"• Mejoras históricas:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"182","text":"• ↑Técnicas de\\Nimagen craneal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"182","text":"• ↑Tecnología\\Nmicrobiológica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"182","text":"• Procedimientos neuroquirúrgicos\\Nmínimamente invasivos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"182","text":"• Tratamiento antibiótico\\Nmejorado [2&&].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"182","text":"• Mortalidad:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"182","text":"• 1960: 40%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"182","text":"• 2010: 15%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"182","text":"• Aspiración estereotáxica: 3% (posible\\Nsesgo de publicación) [2&&].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"182","text":"• Secuelas neurológicas: 70% sin o mínimas secuelas\\Nneurológicas, falta de datos sobre evaluación\\Nfuncional/neuropsicológica a largo plazo [2&&].","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"193","parent":"0","text":"Referencias:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"0","text":"2. Brouwer, M. C., & van de Beek, D. (2017).\\NCurr Opin Infect Dis, 30:129–134. DOI:10.\\N1097/QCO.0000000000000334.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"0","text":"28. Estudio de cohorte retrospectivo\\Nsobre ruptura intraventricular.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"0","text":"29. Evaluación del tratamiento\\Nanticonvulsivo profiláctico en\\Nlesiones ocupantes de espacio.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"197","parent":"0","text":"Conclusión sobre\\NAbscesos Cerebrales","guid":"wNLiutS79Ah4ii-xR8r9yw","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"0","text":"1. Incidencia:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"199","parent":"198","text":"• Enfermedad rara: Pocos estudios\\Ndisponibles para evaluar la incidencia\\N[1&&, 2&&, 11&, 25&].","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"200","parent":"0","text":"2. Causas más\\Nfrecuentes:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"201","parent":"200","text":"• Microorganismos:\\NStaphylococcus y Streptococcus\\Nspp.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"202","parent":"200","text":"• Vías de acceso\\Nal cerebro:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"203","parent":"200","text":"• Diseminación\\Nhematógena","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"200","text":"• Infección sinusal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"200","text":"• Trauma","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"200","text":"• Neurocirugía\\N[1&&, 2&&].","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"207","parent":"0","text":"3. Avances recientes:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"208","parent":"207","text":"• Factores de riesgo genéticos:\\NAnálisis de polimorfismos [8&].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"207","text":"• Duración de tratamientos\\Nantibióticos: Evaluación de\\Ncursos más cortos [19].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"207","text":"• Tratamiento con oxígeno hiperbárico:\\NEstudios en desarrollo [27].","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"211","parent":"0","text":"4. Mejoras en el pronóstico\\N(últimos 50 años):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"212","parent":"211","text":"• Factores clave:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"213","parent":"211","text":"• Mejora en técnicas de\\Nimagen cerebral","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"211","text":"• Procedimientos neuroquirúrgicos\\Nmínimamente invasivos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"215","parent":"211","text":"• Tratamiento antibiótico\\Nprotocolizado [1&&, 2&&].","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"216","parent":"0","text":"5. Necesidades futuras:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"217","parent":"216","text":"• Estudios multicéntricos prospectivos y ensayos\\Nclínicos aleatorizados: Par